<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li><strong>The Society of the Second Hytoth:</strong> Inactive. A small occult organization active in Canada during the late 1800s. Reorganized into the Church of the Second Hytoth in 1900 following its encounter with the Second Messenger.</li>
</ul>
</div>
